(97322, 'linux, linux-snapdragon vulnerabilities (USN-3208-1)', 'linux，linux-snapdragon漏洞（USN-3208-1）', 'Ubuntu主机缺少一个或多个安全补丁。', '更新受影响的包：\n\n  - Installed package : linux-image-4.4.0-62-generic_4.4.0-62.83\n    Fixed package     : linux-image-4.4.0-64-generic_4.4.0-64.85\n\n  - Installed package : linux-image-generic_4.4.0.62.65\n    Fixed package     : linux-image-generic_4.4.0.64.68\n'),
